Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.91,0:00:08.61,Default,,0,0,0,,人好多啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.51,0:00:12.25,Default,,0,0,0,,请问你们在找什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.45,0:00:16.37,Default,,0,0,0,,欢迎光临
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.39,0:00:19.74,Default,,0,0,0,,你看看 这件绝对合身
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.74,0:00:21.26,Default,,0,0,0,,还有其他的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.98,0:00:31.10,Default,,0,0,0,,是错觉吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.79,0:00:33.18,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起
